name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SpeedRun - Speed Ads On Videos at 16x

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Blaze through and skip ads at 16x speeds! SpeedRun does this with minimal impact to your video watching experience.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
SpeedRun is extremely lightweight and seamlessly integrates to your browser. It's engineered to elevate your online video viewing experience. Tailored for YouTube (& more platforms coming soon!), SpeedRun discreetly accelerates video ads and skips them automatically, empowering you to savor your content with uninterrupted flow. FEATURES: -Extreme ad speeds(16x), -Muting ads, -Takes minimal space, -Auto skips ads, -Minimal to no impact on page, -Seamless intergration, -Hides ad banners,  Removes shorts from your feed, -100% free. No need to block youtube ads anymore.
